Subject: [PATCH v3 16/27] rcar-vin: add functions to manipulate Gen3 CHSEL value
Date: Tue, 14 Mar 2017 20:02:57 +0100
Message-Id: <20170314190308.25790-17-niklas.soderlund+renesas@ragnatech.se>
